Top Movies Search is a free extension that provides an exclusive way of online content searching. Enjoy in one click the latest and fullest information about the news, updates and your search queries.

Our unique search algorithm gives you an opportunity to explore instant answers for all your requests. Along with the user-friendly UI and intuitive design, Top Movies Search New Tab provides an exclusive high level user experience.

You may remove this extension at any time from the chrome extension page.

Visit our website at https://topmoviessearch.com/
Read more about us: https://topmoviessearch.com/about-tab/
Read our Privacy Policy: https://topmoviessearch.com/privacy-policy/
Read our Terms & Conditions: https://topmoviessearch.com/terms-conditions/
